· Evaluates written and verbal communication provided to and received from other modalities regarding continuity of resident care and takes appropriate action;
· Participates in developing a program to facilitate continuity of care when residents are transferred to other nursing facility or the hospital;
· Assumes responsibility for independent study to improve managerial and clinical skills;
· Prepares written reports, reviews records and participates in needed data collection as indicated;
· Adjusts schedule to evaluate staff on evening and night shifts;
